com.github.yeetmanlord.zeta_core.sql

Interface ISQLObjectHandler<SuperType extends ISQL<?>>

  • Type Parameters:
    SuperType - The SuperType is the class that implements ISQL. For example: class SuperClass implements ISQL

    public interface ISQLObjectHandler<SuperType extends ISQL<?>>
    Handler that loads and encodes SQL encodable objects. This is the backbone of the ORM.
    Author:
    YeetManLord

      • load

        SuperType load(Row data)
